# =============================================================================
# Mobile (Expo) environment variables — packages/mobile/.env
# =============================================================================
# Naming rules:
#   EXPO_PUBLIC_*  → Bundled into JS at build time. Readable via process.env
#                    in mobile/shared code. Visible to client — NEVER put
#                    secrets here.
#   No prefix      → Build-time only (used by config plugins / native build
#                    tooling). NOT readable from JS.
#
# IMPORTANT:
#   - Metro caches env at startup. After editing this file, restart Metro:
#       npx expo start --dev-client --clear
#   - Loaded ONLY when Metro is started from packages/mobile/.
#   - DO NOT add VITE_* keys here — those belong in the root .env (web only).
# =============================================================================

# --- Supabase ---
# Currently hardcoded in src/config.ts. Future refactor will use these:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# --- Mapbox public token ---
# Bundled into the JS app for runtime map rendering.
EXPO_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_ACCESS_TOKEN=pk.your-public-token-here

# --- Mapbox download token (build-time only) ---
# Used by @rnmapbox/maps plugin to fetch the native iOS/Android SDK.
# WARNING: secret. Never commit to a public repo.
MAPBOX_DOWNLOAD_TOKEN=sk.your-secret-token-here
